Solars are the most powerful known Aasimon, powerful enough to be deities themselves if they chose it. They are close attendants to a Power or champions of some grand cosmic task. They appear as large, winged humans with metallic skin and hair, with deep and commanding voices. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planescape Monstrous Compendium Appendix One        
              
                    Monster Manual (D&amp;D 3.5)